also. For instance, the Energy Pistol and the Scatter Gun both cost field
charge to fire the weapon. The advantage is, you dont have to purchase
ammo. The disadvantage is making sure you have enough charge left. 
 
Also, the Predator Medicomp healing device drains an immense amount of
field charge when used, generally draining you dry. You always want to use
the Medicomp in combination with the Energy Sift to make sure your not
caught without field charge. 
 
