1 VOTING VOTE VOTES~
&wSyntax: VOTE (Vote Type) [Optional Arguments]
&wSyntax: VOTE (Yea or Yes, Nay or No)
&z
Any player can use VOTE to iniate a mud-wide vote. Only one vote may be
running at a time, and each player may only vote once. Each vote lasts 90
seconds or until every player online has voted.
 
If there is a tie, the vote will automatically fail. If the minimum vote
requirement is not met (50% of the online players), then it also fails. 
 
Administrators can stop a vote at any time, for any reason. Also, anyone
found to be abusing the voting system for questionable purposes can and
will most likely be site banned from the game. You better play fair.
 
