1 WHO~
&RSyntax: &GWHO&w

The who lists all the current players, immortals, and bots. The bots will
be made visible by the &z(&WB&z)&w token next to their name, and immortals
by the &z(&BImmortal&z)&w in the brackets on the left side of their name.

The right set of brackets displays their current statis. If they have been
killed recently, it will show the time left until they respawn. If they
get frozen, are in the menu, or are in the arena, it will show the
appropriate tag.
~

